high_descs: Turn around and take a step, then turn to your left and walk over to the center of the sink counter.
Pick up the dirty purple rag off of the counter.
Turn right and walk over to the rightmost sink.
Place the dirty purple rag into the rightmost sink basin and wash the dirt off of it, then pick up the clean purple rag.
Turn around and walk to the far side of the toilet, then turn back to face the mirror.
Place the clean purple rag on the top of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean purple rag on top of the toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn right, walk to the counter between the sinks, turn left
Pick up the purple cloth on the counter
Turn right, walk to the sink, turn right
Place the purple cloth in the sink, turn on both hot and cold water, wash the cloth, turn off the water, remove the cloth from the sink
Turn left, walk a step, turn left, cross the room, turn left, walk to the towel bar, turn left
turn right and head towards the sinks
pick up the cloth between the sinks
head towards the sink at the right
place the cloth in the sink and wet it
turn around and head towards the water closet
place the wet cloth on the water closet
anns.task_desc: place a wet cloth on the water closet
